---
title: Pan-Seared Tofu with Roasted Potatoes and Creamy Dill Sauce
description: We’ve cracked the code to creating a crowd-pleasing dinner! Everyone loves a good cream sauce – especially one that’s spiked with a touch of mustard and fresh dill! It’s the perfect addition to savoury pan-seared tofu.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-seared-tofu-e03f06a1-fb142ed3.jpg
